snippet.title: REQUISITION VR - Slasher Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1730650/REQUISITION_VR/

DISCORD:
https://discord.com/invite/Wk25aHTkKW

Requisition VR is a 4-player online co-op survival game, set in an apocalyptic world. Run, fight and survive in single-player or co-op mode. Explore abandoned houses and territories, finding guns, knives and other weapons crafted using any objects in the house, from toaster to screwdriver.
